reviewText: I have wanted this movie for a long time and had been unable to find it. I absolutely love it! I am so happy to have found it with English subtitles! You have to have a multi-zone DVD player to play this, or it will not play in the US I bought my DVD player from Amazon too and love it!
I just love Mario Casas and will watch pretty much anything he's in. If that's you as well, I suggest you rent this now.
I loved it. I am a big fan of Mario Casas
I enjoyed this movie. Good acting. I wish it had subtitles.
